{"id": "1421912901316378685", "channel_id": "1300659802455674972", "type": 0, "author_id": "267888098732539914", "author_name": "2ndselna", "author_bot": false, "content": "[Limited-Time Awakening: The Timeless Call]\n● The Self-Select Event Awakening \"The Timeless Call\" is available for a limited time from October 6th, 9:00 to November 3rd, 9:00!\n    ○ You can choose one set from all the limited Awakeners in the \"Faded Legacy\" and the corresponding recommended Wheel of Destiny to add to your selected card pool.\n    ○ After selecting an Awakener, the awakening probability of that Awakener and the corresponding recommended Wheel of Destiny will be increased.\n    ○ The guaranteed rule has been upgraded! Now, every time you obtain 2 SSR rewards, it will include at least 1 selected limited Awakener or the corresponding recommended Wheel of Destiny!\n    ○ When unable to obtain the UP reward, you will now have an equal chance to receive a permanent SSR Wheel of Destiny and an SSR Awakener.\n    ○ If you obtain the same UP reward consecutively twice, the next selected reward obtained through Awaken will definitely be a different UP reward.\n    ○ Keepers who participated in past \"The Timeless Call\" will receive a retrospective compensation base count after the update based on the differences between the new and old guaranteed rules.", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T17:34:13.538000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
